    "Title": "Taking Back Our Goods",
    "Description": "Some upstarts hit my hauling crew on their way to do a delivery. Our tracker is telling us that our ship\u2019s still located at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> so I need you to head over there and get the cargo. You\u2019ll need <EM4>a heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4> to lug the goods from the ship.\n\nI\u2019d bet that whoever attacked us is still there waiting. Arm up, bring your crew, and if you can, give them one from me.\n\nOnce you\u2019ve taken back our goods, drop it off at the freight elevator located at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>.\n\n-Twitch",
